#: ../../source/getting_started/tutorials/dbn_classification.md:1
msgid "DBN 分类：深度信念网络"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/getting_started/tutorials/dbn_classification.md:2
msgid ""
"在 RBM 分类的基础上，进一步构建深度信念网络（Deep Belief Network, DBN），通过堆叠多层 RBM "
"实现更强大的特征学习能力。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/getting_started/tutorials/dbn_classification.md:4
msgid "目标"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/getting_started/tutorials/dbn_classification.md:6
msgid "一、RBM 原理概述"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/getting_started/tutorials/dbn_classification.md:8
msgid ""
"受限玻尔兹曼机（Restricted Boltzmann Machine, RBM）是一种基于能量的概率图模型，由可见层（Visible "
"Layer）和隐层（Hidden Layer）组成，层内无连接，层间全连接。其核心是通过无监督学习学习数据的潜在特征分布。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/getting_started/tutorials/dbn_classification.md:10
msgid "1. 模型结构"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/getting_started/tutorials/dbn_classification.md:12
msgid "**可见层（`v`）**：输入数据的显式表示（如像素值）。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/getting_started/tutorials/dbn_classification.md:13
msgid "**隐层（`h`）**：提取的潜在特征。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/getting_started/tutorials/dbn_classification.md:14
msgid "**权重矩阵（`W`）**：连接可见层与隐层的权重。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/getting_started/tutorials/dbn_classification.md:15
msgid "**偏置**：可见层偏置（`b`）和隐层偏置（`c`）。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/getting_started/tutorials/dbn_classification.md:17
msgid "2. 能量函数与概率分布"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/getting_started/tutorials/dbn_classification.md:19
msgid "RBM 的能量函数定义为："
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/getting_started/tutorials/dbn_classification.md:21
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"\n"
"E(\\mathbf{v}, \\mathbf{h}) = -\\mathbf{v}^T W \\mathbf{h} - "
"\\mathbf{b}^T \\mathbf{v} - \\mathbf{c}^T \\mathbf{h}\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/getting_started/tutorials/dbn_classification.md:25
msgid "联合概率分布通过玻尔兹曼分布给出："
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/getting_started/tutorials/dbn_classification.md:27
msgid ""
"\n"
"\n"
"P(\\mathbf{v}, \\mathbf{h}) = \\frac{ e^{-E(\\mathbf{v}, \\mathbf{h})} "
"}{Z}\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/getting_started/tutorials/dbn_classification.md:31
msgid "其中 $Z$ 为配分函数（归一化因子）。可见层的边缘分布为："
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/getting_started/tutorials/dbn_classification.md:33
msgid ""
"\n"
"\n"
"P(\\mathbf{v}) = \\sum_{\\mathbf{h}} P(\\mathbf{v}, \\mathbf{h})\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/getting_started/tutorials/dbn_classification.md:37
msgid "3. 条件独立性"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/getting_started/tutorials/dbn_classification.md:39
msgid "由于层内无连接，给定可见层时隐层条件独立，反之亦然："
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/getting_started/tutorials/dbn_classification.md:41
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"\n"
"P(h_j=1|\\mathbf{v}) = \\sigma\\left(\\sum_i W_{ij} v_i + c_j\\right)\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/getting_started/tutorials/dbn_classification.md:45
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"\n"
"P(v_i=1|\\mathbf{h}) = \\sigma\\left(\\sum_j W_{ij} h_j + b_i\\right)\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/getting_started/tutorials/dbn_classification.md:50
msgid "其中 $\\sigma(x) = \\frac{1}{1+e^{-x}}$ 为 Sigmoid 激活函数。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/getting_started/tutorials/dbn_classification.md:52
msgid "4. 训练目标"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/getting_started/tutorials/dbn_classification.md:54
msgid "通过最大化似然函数学习参数（`W`, `b`, `c`）。目标函数为负对数似然："
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/getting_started/tutorials/dbn_classification.md:56
msgid ""
"\n"
"\n"
"\\mathcal{L} = -\\sum_{\\mathbf{v}} \\log P(\\mathbf{v})\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/getting_started/tutorials/dbn_classification.md:61
msgid "采用对比散度（CD）算法近似梯度，更新规则为："
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/getting_started/tutorials/dbn_classification.md:63
msgid ""
"\n"
"\n"
"\\Delta W_{ij} = \\epsilon \\left(\\langle v_i h_j "
"\\rangle_{\\text{data}} - \\langle v_i h_j "
"\\rangle_{\\text{recon}}\\right)\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/getting_started/tutorials/dbn_classification.md:68
msgid ""
"其中 $\\epsilon$ 为学习率，$\\langle \\cdot \\rangle_{\\text{data}}$ 和 $\\langle"
" \\cdot \\rangle_{\\text{recon}}$ 分别为数据分布和重构分布的期望。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/getting_started/tutorials/dbn_classification.md:70
msgid "二、整体模块架构与训练模式"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/getting_started/tutorials/dbn_classification.md:72
msgid "代码实现了基于 PyTorch 的深度信念网络（DBN），采用分层架构设计，支持从无监督预训练到有监督学习的完整流程。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/getting_started/tutorials/dbn_classification.md:74
msgid "**模块架构**："
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/getting_started/tutorials/dbn_classification.md:76
msgid "**`DBNPretrainer`**   实现多层 RBM 的堆叠与逐层无监督预训练，提供特征提取接口。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/getting_started/tutorials/dbn_classification.md:79
msgid ""
"**`AbstractSupervisedDBN`**   定义 DBN "
"监督学习的通用接口，用于支持多模式训练策略，包括预训练、微调、分类器训练与预测等抽象方法。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/getting_started/tutorials/dbn_classification.md:82
msgid ""
"**`AbstractSupervisedDBNClassifier`**   基于 `AbstractSupervisedDBN`，实现 "
"PyTorch 下的通用工具方法封装，包括特征提取、分类器集成（逻辑回归、支持向量机以及随机森林等）。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/getting_started/tutorials/dbn_classification.md:85
msgid "**`SupervisedDBNClassification`**   具体分类任务实现、微调网络构建以及训练。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/getting_started/tutorials/dbn_classification.md:88
msgid "**训练模式**："
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/getting_started/tutorials/dbn_classification.md:90
msgid "**无监督模式**：仅预训练，用于特征提取。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/getting_started/tutorials/dbn_classification.md:91
msgid "**分类器模式**：预训练 + 下游分类器训练。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/getting_started/tutorials/dbn_classification.md:92
msgid "**微调网络模式**：预训练 + 网络反向传播微调。"
msgstr ""

